1
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:06,760
My Lord.

2
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:07,960
The barrier set by King Kunmi,

3
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:09,620
I have been unable to break it.

4
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:11,360
You cannot even handle such a small matter.

5
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,960
What use do I have for you?

6
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,760
I have failed in my duty.

7
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:16,120
Please punish me, My Lord.

8
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,780
I will spare your life for now.

9
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:21,080
If you fail to retrieve the Seven-Colored Divine Stone again,

10
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:22,610
you shall end your own life.

11
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,720
To think this person...

12
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:35,520
...broke Yunyuan's barrier with a single strike.

13
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,700
Ling'er, are you alright?

14
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:44,120
Let us take shelter at the Spirit Spring first.

15
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:47,840
Dragon Princess.

16
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,759
Long time no see.

17
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,420
The last time we met...

18
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:52,880
Oh,

19
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:55,120
...was indeed the last time.

20
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,280
It has been a thousand years.

21
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,280
If you do not wish to repeat the past,

22
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:02,540
hand over the Seven-Colored Divine Stone obediently.

23
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,720
Who do you think you are?

24
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:07,240
To demand the Seven-Colored Stone.

25
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,880
All this fighting and killing...

26
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:10,840
...is so unpleasant.

27
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,160
Look at Kunmi.

28
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,400
Life is devastated.

29
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,660
Ruins are everywhere.

30
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,640
These are the very lives you so-called gods

31
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:20,280
are so bent on protecting.

32
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,560
Dragon Princess.

33
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,640
Can you bear to watch them

34
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,040
die in vain

35
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,560
because of you?

36
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:30,820
Since when do demons pity the living?

37
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,160
What a joke.

38
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:34,560
If you did not slaughter the innocent,

39
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:36,180
how would conflict arise?

40
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:38,960
Sister Qingluan,

41
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,890
are you alright?

42
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,320
If you want the Seven-Colored Stone, come to me.

43
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,579
Why hurt the innocent?

44
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:44,760
Innocent?

45
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,160
Mere ants.

46
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:48,560
How can they be innocent?

47
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,680
Humans live less than a hundred years.

48
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,360
To us demons,

49
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,840
who live for millions of years,

50
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:56,480
they are like butterflies in spring,

51
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,720
or cicadas in summer.

52
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,360
Here for but a moment.

53
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,560
Tell me,

54
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:03,040
if a human steps on an ant by the roadside,

55
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,360
would they apologize to it?

56
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,820
All living things in this world are ants.

57
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:10,560
But even ants have the right to live.

58
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,520
You cannot deprive them of it without cause.

59
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:15,120
Hahaha.

60
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,160
Dragon Princess.

61
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,040
You are right.

62
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,160
Even ants have the right to survive.

63
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,020
But we, the myriads of demons,

64
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,560
are denied that very right.

65
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,480
From the moment they are born,

66
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,210
they are destined to be the ants

67
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:33,120
slaughtered by you so-called gods.

68
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:34,690
Ling'er,

69
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,160
do not be deceived by him.

70
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,480
If your Demon Clan had not gone on a killing spree,

71
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,560
why would the tribes unite against you?

72
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,680
You brought this upon yourselves,

73
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,960
yet you blame others.

74
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,520
So what?

75
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,160
Dragon Princess.

76
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,480
I advise you,

77
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:51,079
hand over the Seven-Colored Divine Stone soon.

78
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,760
I may spare your life.

79
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,240
You cannot give it to him.

80
00:03:59,120 --> 00:03:59,560
Ling'er.

81
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,160
Qingluan.

82
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,480
Are you all right?

83
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,380
We're fine.

84
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,960
If I hand over the Seven-Colored Stone,

85
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:10,620
will you really spare the myriad lives of Kunmi?

86
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,490
Ling'er.

87
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,090
You can't give it to him.

88
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,960
If the Demon Tribe gets the Seven-Colored Stone,

89
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,920
the entire Three Realms will be plunged into misery.

90
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,640
Hahaha.

91
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:24,560
You refuse to do this the easy way.

92
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,280
Qingluan,

93
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,280
take Ling'er and leave first.

94
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:31,760
Okay.

95
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,200
Ling'er,

96
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,600
go to the Spirit Spring first.

97
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,240
I'll go help my sworn brother.

98
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,040
Go, quickly.

99
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,640
Why do I need their protection?

100
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:13,200
Why can't I help them?

101
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:17,400
No, I won't be a burden.

102
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:21,560
I want to restore my true form. I want to fight alongside them.

103
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,880
Dragon Gate. I need to find the Dragon Gate.

104
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,520
Dragon Gate, where are you?

105
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,400
Dragon Gate!

106
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:34,040
Where are you? Come out, quickly.

107
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:42,360
Dragon Gate, where on earth are you?

108
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,320
Ancestor Zulong,

109
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:49,840
my husband, Yunyuan,

110
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,960
guarded Kunmi for a thousand years.

111
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,640
Now the Demon Tribe runs rampant,

112
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,880
and the living beings of Kunmi are suffering.

113
00:05:57,880 --> 00:06:00,080
If your spirit is watching from heaven,

114
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,480
please help me find the Dragon Gate.

115
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:05,760
I am willing to sacrifice my body to protect the realm,

116
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,820
and guard the common people of Kunmi.

117
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,600
My child,

118
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,800
are you ready?

119
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,840
Who are you?

120
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,360
Are you talking to me?

121
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,280
Who am I?

122
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:05,000
I am the Ancestral Dragon.

123
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,480
Ancestor Zulong,

124
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,160
You are still alive?

125
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:11,840
I am now but a remnant soul,

126
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:14,880
guarding this place only to wait for the destined one.

127
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,340
Waiting for the destined one.

128
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:20,100
Years ago, I glimpsed the heavenly secrets,

129
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:24,560
and learned that in ten million years, a catastrophe would befall the world.

130
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:27,320
Only a descendant of my Dragon Clan can save it.

131
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:31,200
So when I fell, I gave the Seven-Colored Spirit Pearl to the Dragon Clan to pass down,

132
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:34,560
and extracted a remnant soul to guard inside this Dragon Gate,

133
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,480
waiting for the destined one.

134
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:39,680
Hoping only to leave a glimmer of hope for the Three Realms.

135
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:42,440
Am I the destined one you speak of?

136
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,040
Yes.

137
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,400
My child,

138
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,680
go now.

139
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:50,000
Retrieve the spiritual power and true form that belong to you.

140
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,440
Stop the catastrophe.

141
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:53,300
This is your responsibility.

142
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,159
Ancestor Zulong,

143
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,720
what should I do?

144
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,280
Enter the Dragon Gate.

145
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:04,200
As long as you withstand the tempering of eighty-one bolts of heavenly lightning,

146
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,460
completing the cycle,

147
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:07,440
you will be able to restore your true form,

148
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:09,970
and transform into a supreme spiritual body.

149
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:13,080
But if you cannot withstand the tempering of the heavenly lightning,

150
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,680
your soul will be scattered.

151
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,400
So,

152
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,680
my child,

153
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,000
are you ready?

154
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,360
Ancestor.

155
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:24,040
I am ready.

156
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,480
I will protect all living beings.

157
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:27,880
My friends,

158
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,840
my beloved.

159
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,410
They are all waiting for me.

160
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,289
I must return to their side.

161
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,039
I will fight alongside them.

162
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,840
Since that is the case,

163
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,840
then go forth.

164
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,919
Do not forget what is in your heart.

165
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,760
I can.

166
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,480
With my flesh,

167
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,260
I will protect the common people.

168
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:01,480
Heaven above,

169
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:14,440
deliver my primordial spirit.

170
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:53,000
Congratulations, my child.

171
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:56,040
You have endured the tempering of eighty-one heavenly thunders

172
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,770
and restored your dragon form.

173
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,880
Now,

174
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:03,000
let me give you one last gift.

175
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:07,880
Ancestor Zulong.

176
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,080
What are you doing?

177
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:12,120
I am but a remnant soul.

178
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:15,360
Rather than dissipating into heaven and earth,

179
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:17,600
I would rather aid my child.

180
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:02,240
Ancestor Zulong!

181
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,960
I will not let you down.

182
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,540
I will use my lifetime of cultivation

183
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:09,930
to protect all beings in the Three Realms.

184
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:54,800
I said I would forge a suit of armor for you.

185
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,680
To make you invincible

186
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,920
and keep you safe.

187
00:13:00,560 --> 00:13:01,280
Yunyuan.

188
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,240
I am here.

189
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:21,640
Yunyuan!

190
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:24,840
Everything you do is in vain.

191
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,760
Father!

192
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:30,920
Ling'er, look out!

193
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,000
Father!

194
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,000
Father, wake up.

195
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,640
Father, it's me.

196
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,400
Is it really you, Ling'er?

197
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,640
It is me, Father.

198
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,240
I am your Ling'er.

199
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:43,800
Ling'er.

200
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:45,770
You must be careful of Yunyuan.

201
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,410
He is of the Demon Tribe.

202
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:49,840
Father, don't scare me.

203
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:51,240
Father!

204
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,760
Ling'er...

205
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:55,920
Ling'er!

206
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,720
Father!

207
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:05,200
Father...

208
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:06,920
Ling'er...

209
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,020
Why did you kill my father?

210
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,440
Ling'er, he wasn't your father.

211
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,200
He was the Demon Lord.

212
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,440
I saw it with my own eyes.

213
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,500
How can it be false?

214
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:26,440
Ling'er, listen to me.

215
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,700
You are the Demon Lord.

216
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:29,120
Give my father back!

217
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,400
I'll kill you!

218
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:37,320
Stop!

219
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:38,560
What's going on?

220
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:39,960
Why are you two fighting?

221
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:41,200
He killed my father.

222
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,920
Ling'er, listen to me.

223
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:45,520
That's impossible.

224
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:47,520
Ling'er, isn't there some misunderstanding?

225
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:48,280
King Kunmi.

226
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,840
The next time we meet,

227
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,040
I will take your life.

228
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,040
Let's go.

229
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:56,240
Ling'er!

230
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:57,330
Ling'er!

231
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,970
Brilliant scheme, Your Highness.

232
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:11,730
The Dragon Princess and King Kunmi have turned against each other.

233
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,570
For tens of thousands of years,

234
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:17,240
My time in the Dragon Clan wasn't wasted.

235
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:37,140
It turns out this treasure of the Dragon Clan

236
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:39,210
is a relic of the Ancestral Dragon.

237
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:43,480
It can only be controlled after recognizing a master.

238
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:47,080
But...

239
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:50,560
who will become the master of the Spirit Pearl?

240
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,200
My Lord.

241
00:15:58,200 --> 00:16:00,920
When will I be able to see you again?

242
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:04,520
Lisha.

243
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:06,760
My Lord.

244
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:09,440
Are you all right?

245
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:12,880
I cannot get close to the Spirit Pearl.

246
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:17,800
The Spirit Pearl has recognized the Dragon Clan's princess, Ao Ling, as its master.

247
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,600
You can use Ao Jue's ambition

248
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,650
to snatch the Spirit Pearl.

249
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:23,200
As you command.

250
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,900
The Seven-Colored Stone.

251
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,370
With the Seven-Colored Stone,

252
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:46,200
the day I rule the Three Realms is near.

253
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:55,780
Once the Huangquan Biluo enters the Dragon Clan princess's body,

254
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:59,480
the Spirit Pearl will be mine.

255
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:03,120
Lisha.

256
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:09,079
Bring back my good daughter and the Seven-Colored Divine Stone.

257
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:10,760
As you command.
